{"tid":699080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小不忍 含得撚","createTime":"2018-06-12T08:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T09:34:30.000Z","uid":187227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fab11f0cf6fabd69e480a8e987b33827355d0d93","tid":699080,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"由梁天琦入冊開始<br />\n連登上下就已經討論移民去邊好<br />\n但係亦有人屌鳩呢班想移民嘅人 叫呢班人唔好逃避 反抗中共<br />\n但係其實香港由1997年淪陷開始 就已經冇勝算 <br />\n問心，97嗰陣走咗幾撚多人<br />\n香港人唔好再自欺欺人，有得走就好走<br />\n一切已經由天琦入冊開始幻滅<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅文化起碼可以由呢班離開嘅人一代一代傳承落去，仲有一線生機<br />\n<br />\n相反，留守嘅人嘅子女最後一定會被赤化，變成講蝗語玩抖音嘅蝗<br />\n<br />\n只要我哋呢一代人香晒，就無人會再記得香港嘅文化，取而代之嘅係被中共洗腦嘅一群人<br />\n<br />\n所以，保護香港文化最好嘅方式就係移民<br />\n離開並唔係逃避，而係以退為進<br />\n<br />\n利申：留守香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec69c30b70af0b16c2b163e160ec147b51b5fab","tid":699080,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec99a1861d7f3ce0c093a5ef8c23697bd40396b","tid":699080,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36099c1e2eccd67e45d3caa67f6620c2d570918c","tid":699080,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4e774ba5557a70103181262812bc74ab80929d","tid":699080,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c03e9d3edc957eed31f1517e40d1512db300b30","tid":699080,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d0b4e699553c84